{"id": "1245188553009533080", "channel_id": "1244953236302069761", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "混沌也是可以通關普通7-12\n關鍵造物：群氓之歌、意識銘刻、水手哨\n其他造物，以增加算力上限，狂氣充能\n\n刻印：狂氣充能、催化、妙手、籌算、鐵壁、易傷、虛弱\n\n命格：拉蒙娜帶一張暴食，拉開血量上限。\n\n孕育之母選擇：心眼利刃、高熱區禁入\n\nBoss戰：累積「高熱區禁入」積累2~3回合。\n因為有預備，算力下降，一張臨反就大約813，且boss反擊次數提高，能一次性彈死Boss。\n\n小怪戰：使用打擊，先清除屏障，然後疊加護盾，依靠心眼利刃打死第一隻，給予其他小怪出血（必須有群氓之歌）。", "timestamp": "2024-05-29T01:34:45.522000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-29T06:09:41.925000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1245188551545454662", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-34-17-911_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183089, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244953236302069761/1245188551545454662/Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-34-17-911_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=69cbcd75&is=69ca7bf5&hm=45ec05bcccc8644fd1c4cac38d5175ed39aef57e37fb954a0cdd4a4e3841bd85&"}, {"id": "1245188551797379132", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-34-41-135_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 148419, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244953236302069761/1245188551797379132/Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-34-41-135_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=69cbcd75&is=69ca7bf5&hm=7b4e27f02dc06e8c4538964b92e7041db01423de8fa683c1156a0a84ac2d67df&"}, {"id": "1245188552199897148", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-46-55-414_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 127888, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244953236302069761/1245188552199897148/Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-46-55-414_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=69cbcd75&is=69ca7bf5&hm=bdcdfbd989d6b4bd762c0928dc04a4ccfb01399a12caef5be4b7a5c549004d4c&"}, {"id": "1245188552799551499", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-29-01-46-48-071_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 129826, "url": "https://c